FBIS4-16924 "drsov076_f_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-076 Daily Report 20 Apr 1994 National Affairs New Head of Chernobyl Power Station Appointed New Head of Chernobyl Power Station Appointed MK2004072094 Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA in Russian 20 Apr 94 p 1 MK2004072094 Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [POSTFACTUM report: "New Chernobyl Director"] [Text] Sergey Parashin has been appointed general director of the Chernobyl Atomic Electric Power Station [AES] by the decision of Ukraine's Ministry of Atomic Energy collegium. Before this he worked as deputy director of the Chernobyl AES for economic matters. Taking the position of general director, Sergey Parashin stated that he considers it as one of his main tasks to convince the public that the Chernobyl AES is no less safe than the other nuclear stations of Ukraine.
